# Frame TV Art Mode

Upload images to Samsung Frame TV Art Mode and change matte colors.

## Setup
- TV IP: 10.0.0.31
- Token: 35083488 (stored, persistent)
- Python env: /Users/Modema11434/.local/pipx/venvs/samsungtvws/bin/python
- Library: samsungtvws 3.0.4+ (with SSL support, v3.0.0 以下 SSL 會斷)

## Upload command
/Users/Modema11434/.local/pipx/venvs/samsungtvws/bin/python scripts/upload_to_frame.py <image_path>

## Matte change SOP
1. upload + select_image（TV 顯示預設灰白）
2. change_matte 設定顏色
3. 告知用戶：去電視手動點一下圖片刷新，顏色才會套用

## Available matte colors
black / neutral / antique / warm / polar / sand / seafoam / sage / burgandy / navy / apricot / byzantine / lavender / redorange / skyblue / turquoise
Format: shadowbox_{color} (e.g. shadowbox_sage)

## Notes
- Supported formats: JPEG, PNG
- change_matte alone does NOT auto-refresh TV display

